quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  23,28,"Niwaruhuka hamwe nabo muzoba muri kumwe muri ubwo bwato nuce uvuga uti:- turakengurukiye Imana yaturokoye nabo bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  23,29,"Nuvuge uti:- Muremyi wanje numanure kw’imanuro ry’imigisha yawe kuko ari wewe mwiza w’imanuro"
  23,30,"Ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo icirwa kininiya, mu vy’ukuri ni twebwe tugirira abantu ibibazo"
  23,31,Hanyuma twarazanye inyuma yabo abandi bantu
  23,32,"Tubarungikira intumwa z’Imana zo muribo zibabwira ziti:- nimusenge Imana yanyu y’ukuri kuko atayindi Mana mufise atariyo yonyene rudende gusa, mbega mwebwe ntimuyitinya"
  23,33,"N’abakuru bo mu bantu biwe barahakanye Imana y’ukuri nukutemera ihuriro ry’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi, tubaha n’amatungo y’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi baca bavuga bati:- ntiyari kuba uyu muntu nuko ameze nkamwe kuko n’umuntu afungura muvyo namwe mufungura, nukunywa akanywa muvyo munywako"
  23,34,Nimwamu gamburukira umuntu ameze nkuyo muzoba muri mu bantu b’uruhombo
  23,35,"Mbega abemerera yuko mugihe muzosandaba nukuba ivu n’amagufa, yuko muzozurwa"
  23,36,Ntibizobaho ivyo mwemererwa
  23,37,"Ntakindi atari ubu buzima bwacu bwo ng’aha kw’Isi butuma dupfa n’ukubaho, ntakindi kandi natwe ntituri mubantu bazozurwa"
  23,38,"Ntiyari\tkuba\tuyu\tatari\tuko\tari\tumuntu\tabeshera\tImana\tnatwe ntitumwemera"
  23,39,"Avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje nuntabare kubera yuko bampakanye"
  23,40,"Ivuga iti:- mumwanya mutoyi isase bazoba bari mumaganya"
  23,41,"Baca bahonywa n’ijwi ry’ukuri, nukubagira nk’umwavu, rero iryo honywa ryabo ryarabashikiye abo bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  23,42,Hanyuma munyuma yabo twaciye tuzana abandi bantu